      "value": "<div><p><strong>Trigger</strong> You are about to Cast a Spell that has the Summon trait</p><hr /></div><p>When you use your spellcraft to create or summon things to life, your medium and motif’s styles become noticeable on their form. Your catalyzed spell’s summoned creatures become @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.nlCjDvLMf2EkV2dl]{Quickened} for 1 round, immediately gaining 1 additional action when you cast the spell. They can use this action only to Stride or Strike (or a similar attack, in the event of summoning a swarm, for example). In addition, they share the same proficiency bonus as you to skill checks using your visionary skill.</p><p><strong>Visionary Catalyst</strong> Your summoned creatures become Quickened for 2 rounds instead of 1.</p>"
